### Dependencies Guidance

- Manage dependencies in [pyproject.toml](mdc:pyproject.toml); lock file: [requirements.lock](mdc:requirements.lock)
- Prefer pinned versions for deterministic builds
- Separate optional extras for tools (e.g., dev, test, docs)
- Keep runtime lean; move heavy libs to optional extras where possible
- After updates, validate quality gates and docs sync

